{"tid":2011844,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"【多圖】Wetland Seasons Park第2期示範單位首曝光","createTime":"2020-05-11T09:18:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T10:06:54.000Z","uid":159234,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"47616d6bdc40dd7f148ff439c3c3760435fc025b","tid":2011844,"uid":159234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T09:18:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200511/photo/bkn-20200511170025315-0511_00842_001_01p.jpg?20200511170346\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20200511%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200511170025315-0511_00842_001_01p.jpg%3F20200511170346&h=10792c58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n多個大型新盤蓄勢待發，新鴻基地產(00016)旗下天水圍Wetland Seasons Park第2期，繼上周發布樓書後，今日(5月11日)首度開放示範單位予傳媒預覽，料有機會短期公布開價。<br />\n<br />\n其中參照第12座8樓A2室搭建的一房單位，實用面積304方呎，大廳連接面積22方呎露台，廚房屬開放式設計，單位內預設無線充電裝置。<br />\n<br />\n而根據別墅3的1樓B單位打造的三房大單位，實用面積779方呎，大廳設面積21方呎露台，主人房連套厠，廚房內則備有多用途房。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200511/photo/bkn-20200511170025315-0511_00842_001_02p.jpg?20200511170346\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20200511%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200511170025315-0511_00842_001_02p.jpg%3F20200511170346&h=48678570&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200511/photo/bkn-20200511170025315-0511_00842_001_03p.jpg?20200511170346\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20200511%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200511170025315-0511_00842_001_03p.jpg%3F20200511170346&h=c942e057&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200511/photo/bkn-20200511170025315-0511_00842_001_04p.jpg?20200511170346\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20200511%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200511170025315-0511_00842_001_04p.jpg%3F2020051117